  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's make takoyaki on the Steam! Use your utensils well to make delicious takoyaki! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with up to four players! Reach for the ultimate high score!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Score Attack]</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/11d2c8585d37f1e72542829a7a2aad8b.poster.avif?t=1771462523\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/11d2c8585d37f1e72542829a7a2aad8b.webm?t=1771462523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/11d2c8585d37f1e72542829a7a2aad8b.mp4?t=1771462523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for 1st place on the leaderboards by making as much takoyaki as possible! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Battle]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/729991f62e53d176642fcd34d187f275.poster.avif?t=1771462523\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/729991f62e53d176642fcd34d187f275.webm?t=1771462523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/729991f62e53d176642fcd34d187f275.mp4?t=1771462523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your takoyaki-making mettle against others!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《How to Play》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Fill the holes with batter and ingredients.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Once the takoyaki start to smoke, flip them over!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   If you're too fast or too slow, it's a flop! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Once both sides are well cooked, finish by placing your takoyaki in the box!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's make takoyaki on the Steam! Use your utensils well to make delicious takoyaki! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with up to four players! Reach for the ultimate high score!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Score Attack]</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/11d2c8585d37f1e72542829a7a2aad8b.poster.avif?t=1771462523\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/11d2c8585d37f1e72542829a7a2aad8b.webm?t=1771462523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/11d2c8585d37f1e72542829a7a2aad8b.mp4?t=1771462523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aim for 1st place on the leaderboards by making as much takoyaki as possible! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[Battle]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/729991f62e53d176642fcd34d187f275.poster.avif?t=1771462523\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/729991f62e53d176642fcd34d187f275.webm?t=1771462523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716720/extras/729991f62e53d176642fcd34d187f275.mp4?t=1771462523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your takoyaki-making mettle against others!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《How to Play》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Fill the holes with batter and ingredients.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Once the takoyaki start to smoke, flip them over!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   If you're too fast or too slow, it's a flop! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Once both sides are well cooked, finish by placing your takoyaki in the box!</p>",
